<p><img src="images/photo1.jpg" alt="[Visitors]" align=right>
The Lincoln Museum features permanent exhibits depicting Abraham Lincoln and his lasting impact on the nation. The museum offers a wide range of programming including family activities, research facilities, lectures, re-enactments, Lincoln and Civil War conferences and exhibit openings. The musuem contains 11 galleries of exhibits, four theaters, computerized hands-on exhibits, maps and displays and priceless artifacts.</p>


<p>Established in 1928, The Lincoln Museum is the world's largest museum dedicated to the life and times of Abraham Lincoln. It is owned and operated by the Lincoln National Foundation.</p>

<p>Tour The Lincoln Museum at <a href="http://www.TheLincolnMuseum.org">http://www.TheLincolnMuseum.org</a>.</p>

